---
The Korean prose-correction rules embedded in the workflow are adapted from
im-not-ai (Humanize KR, epoko77-ai) and draw on Korean translation-studies
scholarship and KatFishNet (ACL 2025, arXiv:2503.00032). Pipeline structure is an
homage to Claude Code's deep-research workflow.

Portions adapted from im-not-ai, Copyright (c) epoko77-ai, released under the
MIT License (https://github.com/epoko77-ai/im-not-ai). The above MIT permission
and warranty-disclaimer notice applies equally to those portions.
